  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The boss from on the job, you know, was very happy with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it made it easier on me, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was by about 20-- 20 or 21. '39, 21. 21 I was, 21 going on 22.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they started the war in '41 with the Russians and the Germans, so then it started to be very bad with food because the Russians said that we have to feed the army first, you know, which they had to, and they did.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the civilian population was very-- had to struggle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to buy, nothing to even-- and those restaurants from the-- from the factory restaurants, you know, it was very little food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the food got worst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The quality of food was got worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then, if they gave you cabbage soup, which is a favorite of the Russians, that cabbage [INAUDIBLE], so you get two pieces of cabbage and then all water.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the cabbage was a rotten cabbage with worms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you had to eat it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to take the worms out, those little white worms, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you had to take it out and-- and sip the water, so-- to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we saw that's getting not good, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were thinking, my brother and I, how to go a little farther from the Germans because it looks like the Germans-- we read in the paper that the Germans getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
